# Ignore everything in this directory.
#
# Obsidian writes live runtime state here (cache, cookies, session data, etc.)
# that should never be committed.
#
# obsidian.json is intentionally NOT tracked. It is generated at activation
# time by the nix module (modules/programs/obsidian/default.nix) via
# home.activation.obsidianVaultConfig, which writes the vault path as
# $HOME/Documents/personal — correct for whichever user runs darwin-rebuild.
# Committing it would hardcode a single user's home directory path.
*
